it.unitn.lifecoach.model

Class Nutrient

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unitn.lifecoach.model.Nutrient

  • public class Nutrient
extends Object
    Represents a nutrient object. It contains the values of this nutrient of a specific product. The nutrients are retrieved from http://api.foodessentials.com/

 </complexType>
